An end-to-end AI-powered outreach system that automatically scrapes websites, summarizes company information, generates personalized cold emails using LLMs, and sends them with human-like timing.

Built using Groq, Python, BeautifulSoup, and SMTP â€” designed as a clean, modular AI engineering project suitable for professional portfolios and internships.

