ğŸ”§ Setup & Installation
1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Create a .env file
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key_here
EMAIL_ADDRESS=your_email@yourdomain.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_smtp_app_password

3. Run the agent
python main.py

